query:
SELECT mj.id, mj.trackId, mj.status, mj.platform, mj.externalJobId, mj.audioUrl, mj.createdAt,
       t.title as track_title, a.id as album_id, a.title as album_title
FROM musicJobs mj
JOIN tracks t ON t.id = mj.trackId
JOIN albums a ON a.id = t.albumId
WHERE a.id IN (
  SELECT a2.id FROM albums a2
  WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tracks t2 LEFT JOIN audioFiles af ON af.trackId = t2.id 
         WHERE t2.albumId = a2.id AND af.id IS NOT NULL) = 0
)
ORDER BY mj.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 30;
